title: Zephyrus G - Did Asus Deliver?
description:
My review of the Asus Zephyrus G - GA502. This is the best gaming laptop from Asus for thin and light gaming on a budget.
Zephyrus G - https://amzn.to/2Vaq9g8

The GA502 has an AMD Ryzen 7 3750H combined with a GTX 1660 Ti. One of the first gaming laptops using this combination of hardware.
